    text: 'A company is developing a Microsoft Dataverse plug-in.\n\nThe plug-in must create a follow-up task for a new account.\n\nYou add the code that receives context (IPluginExecutionContext) and service (IOrganizationService).\n\nYou need to create the remaining code to insert the follow-up task.\n\nAvailable code blocks:\n\nA.\nEntity followuptask = new Entity("task");\nfollowuptask["subject"] = "Send e-mail to the new customer";\nfollowuptask["regardingobjectid"] = account;\n\nB.\nEntity followuptask = new Entity("task");\nfollowuptask["subject"] = "Send e-mail to the new customer";\nfollowuptask["regardingobjectid"] = account.ToEntityReference();\n\nC.\nEntity account = (Entity)context.InputParameters["Target"];\n\nD.\nservice.Create(followuptask);\n\nE.\nEntity account = (Entity)context.PreEntityImages["Target"];\n\nF.\nservice.Update(followuptask);\n\nArrange the correct three code blocks in sequence.',
