    text: 'A university manages grant applications using a model-driven app.\n\nUsers report that the message on the Grant Application screen is outdated.\n\nBased on the graphic, identify:\n1. Which Power Platform capability the app uses to display the message.\n2. What the app maker should update to prevent the message from displaying.\n\nAVAILABLE VALUES:\nCapability:\n- Business rule\n- Logic app\n- Flow\n- Plug-in\n\nAction:\n- Update the field calculation\n- Update the rollup field\n- Update the automated flow\n- Update the business rule',
