    id: 5185,
    text: 'You are creating technical designs for several complex business processes.\n\nYou need to implement custom business logic based on the requirements.\n\nWhich implementation methods should you use?\n\nIMPLEMENTATION METHODS:\n- Business rule\n- JavaScript code\n- Power Automate flow\n- Plug-in\n\nREQUIREMENTS:\n1. Access current and new values when data is updated.\n2. Run on a schedule.',
