    text: 'A company has a model-driven app that captures applications from prospective students.\n\nYou are asked to create a new reusable custom component by using the Power Apps component framework (PCF).\n\nThe custom component must allow entry of a date of birth and validate that the applicant is not a minor.\n\nYou create the class AdultDatePicker in the TypeScript file Index.ts and the style sheet DatePicker.css.\n\nYou need to define the component to be available only for relevant fields and its properties when used in a form.\n\nHow should you complete the manifest?\n\nAVAILABLE VALUES:\nFor constructor:\n- Index.ts\n- DatePicker.css\n- AdultDatePicker\n\nFor of-type:\n- Enum\n- DateandTime.DateAndTime\n- DateandTime.DateOnly\n\nFor usage:\n- bound\n- input',
